Healing Space Therapy App – Showcase & Overview (Updated)

---

**What is Healing Space?**
Healing Space is a comprehensive mental health companion app for patients and clinicians. It combines AI-powered therapy, clinical tools, gamification, and secure data management in both web and desktop interfaces.

---

**Custom AI Therapy – Niche Focus**
Healing Space is actively training a custom AI therapy bot, designed to go beyond generic models. This bot will:
- Use real, anonymized therapy data (GDPR-compliant)
- Adapt to specific mental health niches and user needs
- Integrate clinician feedback and domain expertise
- Continuously improve through supervised learning and real-world usage

This approach ensures the AI therapist is tailored for your community, providing more relevant, empathetic, and effective support than off-the-shelf solutions.

---

**Key Features for Patients:**
- AI Therapy Sessions: Persistent, context-aware conversations with an AI therapist
- Mood Tracking: Daily logs, sleep, medication, and activity tracking
- CBT Toolkit: Thought records, gratitude journaling, breathing and grounding exercises
- Clinical Assessments: PHQ-9, GAD-7, with score tracking and trends
- Pet Companion: Gamified self-care with a virtual pet and rewards
- Progress Insights: AI-generated summaries, charts, and exportable reports
- Community Support: Safe, moderated forums for sharing and encouragement
- Safety Planning: Crisis detection, safety plans, and emergency resources

**Key Features for Clinicians:**
- Professional Dashboard: Patient management, clinical notes, and risk monitoring
- Appointment Calendar: Visual scheduling, urgency indicators, PDF report generation
- Patient Data Export: CSV, PDF, and FHIR-compliant medical data exports
- AI Summaries: Automated clinical summaries and insights
- Notifications: Automated reminders and alerts
- Audit Logging: Best-effort logging for sensitive actions

---

**Security & Privacy:**
- End-to-end encryption (Fernet)
- Passwords hashed with Argon2/bcrypt/PBKDF2
- GDPR-compliant anonymized training data
- HMAC-signed FHIR exports
- 2FA PIN authentication

---

**Technical Highlights:**
- Dual-mode: Flask REST API (web) + Tkinter GUI (desktop)
- 3 SQLite databases: therapist_app.db, pet_game.db, ai_training_data.db
- Groq LLM integration for advanced AI therapy
- Inline database migrations and auto-backups
- Optional SFTP, Vault, and email integrations

